@startuml data-flow-cqrs
!theme plain

title 数据流图 - CQRS 查询数据流

skinparam backgroundColor #FAFAFA
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam defaultFontName Arial
skinparam packageStyle rectangle
skinparam nodesep 25
skinparam ranksep 50

' === Color Constants ===
!define INPUT_COLOR #E3F2FD
!define COMMAND_COLOR #FFCDD2
!define QUERY_COLOR #C8E6C9
!define STORAGE_COLOR #F3E5F5

' === External Entities ===
rectangle "用户" <<External>> #INPUT_COLOR {
}

' === Process Nodes ===
rectangle "1. Dashboard" <<Process>> #QUERY_COLOR {
}

rectangle "2. API Proxy" <<Process>> #QUERY_COLOR {
}

rectangle "3. OperatorAgent" <<Process>> #QUERY_COLOR {
}

' === Command Side (Write) ===
rectangle "4. Nl2SqlController" <<CQRS Command>> #COMMAND_COLOR {
}

rectangle "5. SqlCoderService" <<CQRS Command>> #COMMAND_COLOR {
}

rectangle "6. SqlExecutorService" <<CQRS Command>> #COMMAND_COLOR {
}

' === Query Side (Read) ===
rectangle "7. OperatorQuery\nController" <<CQRS Query>> #QUERY_COLOR {
}

rectangle "8. OperatorQuery\nService" <<CQRS Query>> #QUERY_COLOR {
}

rectangle "9. IndicatorQuery\nController" <<CQRS Query>> #QUERY_COLOR {
}

rectangle "10. IndicatorQuery\nService" <<CQRS Query>> #QUERY_COLOR {
}

' === Data Stores ===
database "11. MySQL\noperator_db" <<DataStore>> #STORAGE_COLOR {
    artifact [operator_info\n写/读]
    artifact [site_info\n读]
    artifact [indicator_info\n读]
    artifact [operator_summary\n读]
}

rectangle "SQLCoder LLM" <<External>> #INPUT_COLOR {
}

' === Command Side Flows (NL2SQL) ===
4 -> 5 : 自然语言查询
5 -[#red,dashed]-> SQLCoder LLM : 生成 SQL
SQLCoder LLM -[#red,dashed]-> 5 : SQL 语句
5 -> 6 : SQL 语句
6 -> 11 : INSERT/UPDATE/DELETE
6 <-- 11 : Result

' === Query Side Flows (Read) ===
7 -> 8 : 查询请求
8 -> 11 : SELECT operator_info\nSELECT site_info
11 ---> 8 : Operator 数据
11 ---> 10 : Indicator 数据
8 --> 7 : Operator 结果
10 --> 9 : Indicator 结果

' === Response Flow ===
7 --> 3 : 查询结果
9 --> 3 : 查询结果
3 --> 2 : 汇总结果
2 --> 1 : HTTP Response
1 --> 用户 : 可视化展示

' === Input Flow ===
用户 -[#blue,dashed]-> 1 : 读取请求\n"查看北京联通数据"

' === CQRS Label ===
note top of 4
  **CQRS Command Side**
  处理写操作和 NL2SQL 命令
  调用 SQLCoder 生成 SQL
end note

note top of 7
  **CQRS Query Side**
  处理读操作
  优化查询性能
end note

' === Data Flow Labels ===
note bottom of 11
  **Data Flow:**
  - Command: Write -> Execute -> Validate -> Store
  - Query: Read -> Query -> Aggregate -> Return
end note

legend right
|= Path |= Type |= 说明 |
| Red dashed | LLM Call | SQLCoder 生成 SQL |
| Green | Query Flow | 读操作流程 |
| Blue dashed | User Input | 外部输入 |
endlegend

@enduml